  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add sliced onion and minced garlic; sauté until onion is translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Toss in the fresh grape tomatoes and stir-fry for 2 minutes, letting them soften slightly.",
    "Add the fermented grape tomatoes, smoked paprika, cumin, sea salt, and pepper; cook for 3 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Stir in the fresh spinach, letting it wilt for 2 minutes.",
    "Drizzle lime juice, sprinkle chopped oregano, and stir to combine.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning if necessary.",
    "Serve immediately, optionally with a side of cauliflower rice."
